notes ""
{
NPCText "Message sent by: 00srj@GAInet:HQ. Copy: Mr Voight, I'm sure you already know about the hidden flaws in ME. Our new CEO finds it hard to believe nobody on your team knew about them before release. He's going to want to talk to all of you. You better get your story straight."
